snippet.title: The Dungeon of Naheulbeuk: The Amulet of Chaos - DLC Trailer "Ruins of Limis" -  English version
snippet.description:
The Ruins of Limis are ready for you, adventurers… And there's more!

You can now get the Season Pass for The Amulet of Chaos, which includes the Ruins of Limis and two upcoming DLCs!

Find it all here: https://bit.ly/3bPGsKk

💻  DLC available on PC & Mac
🕹️ Included in the Chicken Edition from 24/06

Until then, find Dungeons of Naheulbeuk: The Amulet of Chaos on:
✔️ The website: https://bit.ly/3bxCk22
✔️ Steam: https://bit.ly/3yxKW2bn
✔️ Epic Games Store: https://bit.ly/3p17wuO
✔️ GOG.com: http://bit.ly/3qBGbPO

Remember to follow us on social media:
On Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Naheulbeuk.JeuVideo
On Twitter: https://twitter.com/Naheulbeuk_Jeu
